### List reservations for a program

@PROGRAM_ID = c9c4183f-da12-4428-846a-ffd434a75bed
@DONOR_ID = 02986c41-a839-4196-8a43-d6bf253a2bc5
@RESERVATION_ID = 0e768895-5ad7-4846-82a6-450dcee61cea
GET http://localhost:5000/api/programs/{{PROGRAM_ID}}/stalls

### Reserve a stall for a donor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/programs/{{PROGRAM_ID}}/stalls/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donorId": "{{DONOR_ID}}"
}

### Set stall capacity (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/programs/{{PROGRAM_ID}}/stalls/capacity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "capacity": 12
}

### Cancel a stall reservation
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/{{RESERVATION_ID}}/cancel

### Check-in a stall reservation
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/{{RESERVATION_ID}}/check-in

### Scan QR to check-in (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/scan-qr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeRef": "STALL-{{PROGRAM_ID}}-3"
}

### Cancel expired stalls (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/admin/update-expired

### Get stall application by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/applications/{{APPLICATION_ID}}

### List stall applications for program (admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/programs/{{PROGRAM_ID}}/stalls/applications

### Stall application stats (admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/programs/{{PROGRAM_ID}}/stalls/applications/stats

### Scan stall application QR (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/applications/scan-qr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeValue": "{{QR_CODE_VALUE}}",
  "adminId": "{{ADMIN_ID}}",
  "notes": "Checked in at gate"
}

### Cancel expired stall applications (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/applications/admin/update-expired

### Get reservation (includes QR fields)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stalls/{{RESERVATION_ID}}
